    dc:creator "Turrisi, Giuseppe Fabrizio; Watanabe, Kyohei" ;
    dc:date "2011" ;
    dc:title "Description of two new Asian Pristaulacus Kieffer 1900 (Hymenoptera: Aulacidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202222>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202224>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202223>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202225>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202226> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202222>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Pristaulacus japonicus Turrisi & Watanabe, sp. n. (holotype Ƥ, Japan): 1, habitus; 2, head dorsal view; 3, head frontal view; 4, head lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/202222/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202224>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8 – 11. Pristaulacus japonicus Turrisi & Watanabe, sp. n. (holotype Ƥ, Japan): 8, wings; 9, mid and hind coxae, ventral view; 10, hind tarsus, lateral view and detail of tarsal claws; 11, metasoma, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/202224/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202223>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 7. Pristaulacus japonicus Turrisi & Watanabe, sp. n. (holotype Ƥ, Japan), mesosoma: 5, dorsal view; 6, lateral view; 7, propodeum, latero-posterior view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/202223/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202225>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12 – 15. Genital capsule of Pristaulacus japonicus Turrisi & Watanabe, sp. n. (paratype ♂, Japan) (12 – 13) and, P. gibbator (Thunberg 1822), specimen from Sweden (NHRS) (14 – 15). 12 – 14, paramere, inner view; 13 – 15, detail of lamina volsellaris, inner view, and penis valve, outer view. Scale bars = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/202225/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202226>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16 – 17. Habitat of findings of Pristaulacus japonicus Turrisi & Watanabe, sp. n. (Japan: Mt. Ontake-san, Hakkaisan): 16, general view; 17, bark-less tree of Larix kaempferi Sargent, place of findings of aulacids." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/202226/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

